/**
 * \page BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient Button VRPN Client
__________________________________________________________________

Detailed description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Description|
 This box connects to an external VRPN device and translate a button 
 information into BRAND_NAME stimulations, so that it can be used in 
 BRAND_NAME applications.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Description|
__________________________________________________________________

Outputs description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Outputs|
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Outputs|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Output1|
This output is used to import data from the VRPN server to a BRAND_NAME stream
of stimulations.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Output1|
__________________________________________________________________

Settings description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Settings|
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Settings|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Setting1|
 The name of the button device to connect to.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Setting1|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Setting2|
 This setting specifies the stimulation that is sent each time the button device 
 changes of state to become activated (set on 'ON').
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Setting2|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Setting3|
 This setting specifies the stimulation that is sent each time the button device 
 changes of state to become deactivated (set on 'OFF').
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_ButtonVRPNClient_Setting3|
